{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very interestingly, the question wasn't asked for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they asked for my brother, who was wearing the fasces sign, are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, go against the wall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stay against the wall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I insisted hey, that's my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I want to be with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not only the closeness, but suddenly we couldn't-- I couldn't figure out, and brash, 15-and-a-1/2-year-old, you know, who is afraid of nothing and nobody, went and stood with my brother.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And suddenly, people, more and more people were pushed against the wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then probably a couple of hours later, we were marched into the headquarters of the Budapest Police Station.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Which was a big courtyard, it's nothing else but a courtyard, building all around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And more and more and more and more people came there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what I would like to tell you, that Budapest is basically-- or effectively, I think so-- the same geographical height as northern part of the United States, like Buffalo, Syracuse, or whatever you want to call-- Albany, I mean, New York State wise.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was cold, miserable, rainy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, just a bad day of-- of being outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Although you know, like we had our jackets, our coats.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Side We had coats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Definitely at that time, March, we had coats.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and but we had only our school bag, the school's-- right now it's one-- once again fashionable that you have the bag-- backpack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At that time, it was the backpack was our school bag, and our lunch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had no idea, but we suddenly realized that everybody in that courtyard was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "More and more and more and more and more people were pushed in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
